post_text: The main job of the Judge/Executive is to oversee the responsible use of your tax money. Because of the 2008 recession, our county finances greatly suffered. When I took office in 2014, I used my business experience to stop the decline of our financial situation. I am happy to report that our county surplus has steadily grown each year that I have been in office. I need your VOTE on November 6th to keep Jessamine County financially strong.
